<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6375312>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Number of Neotropical species by genus in the family Pompilidae. Color bars follow subfamilial classification: Pepsinae in green, Pompilinae in purple, Notocyphinae in blue, Ceropalinae in red. Braunilla es the new name for Balboana (Wasbauer & Kimsey, 2019b)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6375312/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6375314>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Number of species for subfamilies: Ceropalinae, Notocyphinae, Pepsinae and Pompilinae. Braunilla es the new name for Balboana (Wasbauer & Kimsey, 2019b)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6375314/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

